show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/UV7Uqw
show.description: Lucilia's ordinary life hides an extraordinary obsession. By day, she's just another employee—but behind closed doors, she secretly pines for her charismatic boss, Ricardo. When her boyfriend Jeremy uncovers a trove of Ricardo's photos and unsent love letters on her phone, Lucilia's carefully compartmentalized worlds begin to collide. As suspicions flare and boundaries blur, an explosive affair ignites between Lucilia and Ricardo, pulling all three into a dangerous triangle of desire, deception, and impossible choices. How far will obsession take her, and who will get burned when passion finally boils over?
